result.notes:
Ichthyoplankton samples were collected over three separate periods during a 
survey in an area in the central North Sea. As part of a number of survey 
objectives the distribution of early stage plaice eggs was investigated. This 
data consists of the numbers of plaice eggs and the larvae of herring and 
sprat identified from the main net samples. Positional data and volumes 
filtered are included.
